---
title: Cheesy Black Bean & Veggie Enchiladas with Sour Cream & Radish Salad
description: Enchiladas – what could be more fun? Take one part tasty beans and veg, one part soft tortillas, then combine them and top the whole thing with melty cheesy goodness. With a fresh radish salad, this is a sure-fire winner.

*Unfortunately, this
week's red kidney
beans were in short
supply, so we've
replaced them with
black beans. Don't
worry, the recipe will
be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow
your recipe card!*
